# Commit-Message Format

Use this template:
```
<type>(<scope>): <short description>  

<body>               # optional, 1–2 sentences  
<footer>             # optional, e.g. “Closes #123”
```
- **type**: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore  
- **scope**: the area of change (e.g., “auth”, “ui”, “api”)  
- Limit the first line to fifty characters.
